UserCode.UpdatableTokens
Class FishFood

java.lang.Object
  UserCode.UpdatableTokens.FishFood
All Implemented Interfaces:
IUpdatable, IDisplayable
public class FishFood
extends java.lang.Object
implements IUpdatable, IDisplayable

This class represents Fish Food. Instances of this class can be placed into the aquarium by left-clicking the mouse. The food should fall to the bottom of the aquarium and rest there. If the food collides with a fish token at any point, it should be 'eaten', removing it from the aquarium.

Version:
22-02-2021, 0.4
Author:
Kristopher Randle
